nodes.title: Positive Text
widgets_values: A traditional hand‑painted portrait rendered with visible, layered brush strokes on a textured leather surface. Rich acrylic-like pigments in warm earthy tones, subtle color blending, soft yet defined edges, delicate highlights and fine whisker‑like lines, realistic but stylized with painterly depth and surface grain. Emphasis on natural brush texture, layered impasto effects, and handcrafted artisanal quality. Consistent, repeatable style across all subjects.
